dataset.name: ICE UK Natural Gas, June 2020 (MM2020)
dataset.description:
Contract Size:1,000 therms per day per period

Deliverable Good:Matching Acquiring and Disposing Trade Nominations (buyer from ICEU, seller to ICEU) are input by buyer and seller to National Grid via Gemini before 18:30 on the business day prior to the commencement of the delivery period. Delivery takes place in kilowatt-hours (29.3071 kilowatt hours per therm).

Tick Size:Sterling and pence per therm

Pricing Unit:5000 therms per day

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
